subject: World Cup (Skiing)
Speedskating
Skiing
lead_paragraph: Lindsey Vonn of the United States had the best giant slalom result of her career, finishing third behind Germany’s Viktoria Rebensburg in a World Cup race in Spindleruv Mlyn, Czech Republic.
